public interface OrderProductRepository extends org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<OrderProduct,OrderProductId>
Repository interface for OrderProduct entities.

This interface provides CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for OrderProduct entities. It extends CrudRepository, which is a Spring Data interface that simplifies data access operations.
